			<div style="font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); font-family: Raleway, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><h1 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 25px; margin: 5px 0px;"><font color="#0000ff">JCPS COVID-19 Information</font></h1></div>
<div style="font-size: small; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); box-sizing: border-box; width: auto;">
<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Raleway, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium;"><font color="#0000ff">Jones County Schools is committed to the safety and security of our students and staff. We continue to remain in regular contact with the Jones County Health Department and NC DHHS as well as NCDPI.  We are working closely with state and local officials on COVID-19 impacts to our school community.</font></span></p>
<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Raleway, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box;"><font color="#0000ff"><span style="font-size: medium;"><u>Stop the Spread!</u></span><br></font></p>
<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box;"><font face="Raleway, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="3" color="#0000ff">The most important thing students, staff and families can do now to help stop the spread of germs is continue to follow everyday preventive actions recommended by the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) and the North Carolina Department of Health and Human Services (NCDHHS).  Their links are below:</font></p>
<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box;"></p>
<ul style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
<li style="margin-left: 15px;"><font color="#0000ff"><span style="font-family: Raleway, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: medium;"><a target="_blank" href="https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-nCoV/index.html" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-nCoV/index.html&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1584707795899000&amp;usg=AFQjCNHbxzlZFDG8LRLp5x7ZGH3BDLmpVQ" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">https://www.cdc.gov/<wbr>coronavirus/2019-nCoV/index.<wbr>html</wbr></wbr></a></span><br></font></li>
<li style="margin-left: 15px;"><font color="#0000ff"><font face="Raleway, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="3"><a target="_blank" href="https://www.ncdhhs.gov/divisions/public-health/coronavirus-disease-2019-covid-19-response-north-carolina" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.ncdhhs.gov/divisions/public-health/coronavirus-disease-2019-covid-19-response-north-carolina&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1584707795899000&amp;usg=AFQjCNEs3FD-FdN8xdXrHakgU0BgPdIWNg" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">https://www.ncdhhs.gov/<wbr>divisions/public-health/<wbr>coronavirus-disease-2019-<wbr>covid-19-response-north-<wbr>carolina</wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></a></font><span style="font-family: Raleway, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: medium;"> </span><br></font></li>
</ul>
<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></p>
<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: Raleway, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: medium;"><font color="#0000ff">Remember the key to prevention is to practice good hygiene.</font></span></p>
<blockquote style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><span style="font-family: Raleway, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: medium;"><ul style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
<li style="margin-left: 15px;"><font color="#0000ff">Wash hands regularly.<br></font></li>
<li style="margin-left: 15px;"><font color="#0000ff">Stay away from those who are sick, and stay home if you are sick.<br></font></li>
<li style="margin-left: 15px;"><font color="#0000ff">Clean and disinfect frequently touched objects and surfaces.<br></font></li>
<li style="margin-left: 15px;">
<font color="#0000ff">Cover your cough or sneeze with a tissue.<font color="#0000ff"></font></font><font color="#0000ff"></font>
</li>
</ul>
